reviewText: As far as the action, story and production goes, all three films are just right. My only beef is with the packaging. First off, each film comes on its own disk and is reproduced well. However, 'The Enforcer' comes in an English dub only. The original Cantonese with subtitles would have been much more preferable. As many dubs go, it sounds kind of silly at times. Nonetheless, the action is fine...even funny.
